Flags:
+-    FEcho                - FileEcho
++    InFile=dir           - Store all incoming files to dir
++-   Rules=fname          - Echo rules file name
++    FidoRules=Yes|No     - Send rules to fido side
+-    ModU=addr            - pre-moderated @UUCP side
+-    ModF=addr            - pre-moderated @FIDO side
++    Approved=u-addr      - Add 'Approved' headline
++    Distrib=dom          - Add 'Distribution' headline
+++   Dir=FU|UF|Both|None  - Direction of conversion

+-	  FHold=directory      - Directory to search for data files (for TIC)

